edu.cnm.deepdive.ironorimgtransform.model.dao

Interface ImageDao


  • public interface ImageDao
    Declares basic CRUD operations for Image instances in the local database, using Room annotations.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      int delete(Image... images)
      Deletes one or more Image instances from local database.
      List<Image> findAll()
      Selects and returns all Image instances in the local database, sorting the result in descending id order.
      Image findFirstById(Long id)
      Selects and returns the single Image instance (or null) for the specified Date.
      List<Image> findGroupByTransform(long transform)
      Selects and returns all images changed by a particular transform type Image instances in the local database, sorting the result in descending id order.
      List<Image> findHistory(long limit)
      Selects and returns a chosen history Image instances in the local database, sorting the result in descending id order.
      List<Long> insert(Image... images)
      Inserts one or more Image instances into the local database.
      long insert(Image images)
      Inserts one Image instances into the local database.
      List<Long> insert(List<Image> images)
      Inserts a List of Image instances into the local database.

        Returns:
